// ch05 §5.12: a lambda expression desugars to an anonymous,
// compiler-synthesized class -- a by-value capture (`[x]`) is an
// ordinary owned member. Calling the closure immediately (an IIFE) needs
// no name for the closure's own unnameable type.
int main() {
    int x = 5;
    return [x]() { return x; }();
}
